        "term": 1,
        "title": "Term 1",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "recybHMjsgNYk1dAF",
            "term": 1,
            "sort": "",
            "content": "[ ] Watch some of the bay and harbour [webcams](https://tourismtofino.com/plan-your-trip/weather-webcams/) located in Tofino on Vancouver Island. \n[ ] Try these [classic Canadian recipes](https://canadianfoodfocus.org/in-your-kitchen/classic-canadian-dishes/) from the provinces you are studying."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "term": 2,
        "title": "Term 2",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "recCCxwUqHR40Ao13",
            "term": 2,
            "sort": "",
            "content": "[ ] [View this map ](https://canadaoceanmap.ca/#)of Canada's ocean and freshwater system. \n[ ] [This video](https://storymaps.arcgis.com/stories/95c8dfc9d1584d459e7e6c6f84422673) looks at how the cycle of the seasons affects the way we connect with the land, through the lenses of both the Métis and the Woodland Cree Nations. \n[ ] [Watch a trip](https://youtu.be/OH3vU2WP89U?si=cxw9-IskQQ5-9gmO) through the Canadian Rockies with this family."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "term": 3,
        "title": "Term 3",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "recPOlP84Dku8MQhl",
            "term": 3,
            "sort": "",
            "content": "[ ] [Enjoy this video](https://youtu.be/1Lnw6tsDg3w?si=-cNHN6piKAhIlbH_) about Niagara Falls. \n[ ] [Learn some fun facts ](https://youtu.be/MhTxCncUgC4?si=qC-2PI80fiw5AoEk)about Quebec. \n[ ] Use what you've learned about flags to [create your own flag](https://justfamilyfun.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Flag-Outlines.pdf) for your family, team, or town."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
